Package Controller

Class Controller

  • java.lang.Object
    • Controller.Controller
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.util.Observer
    public class Controller
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.util.Observer
    our program adapts the "MVC" pattern - Model, View, Controller. this class represents the "Controller". the brain of the MVc pattern. the controller knows all the classes it needs for the program, in particular the board(view) and game(model).
    Author:
    YuvalAmar and Dvir Hacohen
